{"tid":1554741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【海外文宣戰線】一個外國巴同我講ge野 The enemy is the communist party.","createTime":"2019-09-09T05:51:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T03:35:44.000Z","uid":272188,"like":71,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"1d3876140ffcd348bc2177e78d3902e330ebb4bf","tid":1554741,"uid":272188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T05:51:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">The enemy is not the police, not the Hong Kong government. The enemy is the communist party. So aim for the party. </span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢排同緊個外國巴傾緊香港發生緊ge事 <br />\n佢絕對支持我地做緊咩野 由返送中 到5 demands no one less.<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過吾太認同用魔法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重點不過吾係呢到 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重點係 佢要我地全世界知道 果枝槍吾應該指向班狗 個政府 而係中共</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而加好明顯已經係由中共控制緊ge軍政府 所以佢好吾明仲點解日日圍狗屋 去撚狗 去撚港鐵 點解要去送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為佢話 <span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;Don&rsquo;t target the solider; Target the general, whose name is the communist party&rdquo; </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正正因為而加好明顯大陸send左一炸人落黎 <span style=\"color: red;\">同埋而加係軍政府 攬炒係遲左ge事</span> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁我地還點ready攬炒 點解吾做多d野？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n佢講左好多方法 其中一個而加要做ge係加速同全世界講 中國可以對你做d咩 中國吾同香港keep promise佢仲可以吾同你地吾keep咩promises <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實而加全世界都聽到你地 知道發生咩事 個問題係 你地日日講咩basic human rights. 佢地聽到 政客聽到 佢地可以用黎食? <span style=\"color: red;\">要解決 你就要令到外國市民都覺得嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 覺得中共係所有問題ge中心 由市民再逼政客去對抗中共</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要去做 就係用文宣 由一個大idea 一個basic idea開始 再由呢d idea寫一個story 個故事係可以令人有共嗚 <span style=\"color: red;\">比佢地知道 中共其實吾單係影響緊香港 係搞埋你地 比佢地知道 係wor 中共死 世界先好 而吾係因為香港想中共死 所以我地先幫佢 </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而吾係比佢地食花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地更加吾可以只係對住英國 美國做文宣 要做 就要做到全世界枝槍指向中共 想中共要死</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個大idea要用黎做文宣ge baseline 做故事大鋼 例如<br />\n對英國就宣傳&rdquo;Winston Churchill didn&rsquo;t back down to Hitler because British never yield to dictator.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n對義大利就講&rdquo;The Chinese is cracking down the Catholic in China. God doesn&rsquo;t give democracy. God gives us power to stand up to face satan.&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n對德國就講&rdquo;Hitler killed Jewish like China slaughter Tibet.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n對美國吾同人就講吾同野<br />\n對Hippes 就係 &ldquo;The perfect society is a place with freedom, just and fairness; and China has offered nothing but dictatorship.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n對Christian就係&rdquo;God appointed Trump as persistent to fight for the cunning and calculative China who steal millions of jobs from Christians, blue collar, day in day out Americans. God will help Trump to win this war. God bless America.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n對Atheists 就係&rdquo;As a modern society, basic human right is freedom of speech, religion and multiculturalism and China hates human rights.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n再例如 如果要再細分d 講個英國story就去吾同social media e.g Twitter, Reddit, Quora, Facebook, Linkedin 去到Tinder and Grindr 講一個story <span style=\"color: red;\">因為只有一個故事 人地先感受到個問題 而吾係一味比facts</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay 1: Look at how Hong Kong is fighting the extreme power is actually heart breaking. <br />\n<br />\nDay 2: What have we been doing so far to fight for democracy in our land against that fucking Borris Johnson?? We live in a place in democracy and now we lost it. WTF people??<br />\n<br />\nDay 3: We shell never yield to extreme control. The government should listen to us. Borris Johnson should listen to us. China should listen to Hong Kong people. This is democracy. We stand as Winston Churchill once stood. Fight for power; fight for democracy. <br />\n<br />\n咁樣再加緊宣傳個idea. <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">又例如 吾係只係講#Chinazi  so you have to help us. <br />\n<br />\n而係講德國發展商大部分都係中國ge 你真係想為一班Nazi去做份工? A country that has genocide a whole place like Hitler?</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">佢指出 香港人一直靠hard power. It is time to change. Don&rsquo;t underestimate soft power.</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">We have been giving people hope. Give them Fear. Fear control the people and change behaviour.</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Fear brings 2 millions of you guys together. Use fear to bring the whole world together to up against the party. &ldquo;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&ldquo;If you can be water, be something more. Be a river.&rdquo;</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢最尾學左句中文講 香港人 加油 我真係喊晒出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果真係有興趣 可以再tg講"},{"pid":"959b0c50132d2f1638d75e3c115117970a71c658","tid":1554741,"uid":16846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T05:53:41.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;Winston Churchill didn&rsquo;t back down to Hitler because British never yield to dictator.&rdquo;如果英國佬覆你話而家已經有就好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda31843ffe023a1cb3524c10be1f46008774ce8","tid":1554741,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:00:46.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"021df4ea07d67c02dca9c2f215d01dfe86b30e96","tid":1554741,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:01:08.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"4d03e28f2f3b3ad89293987b5f3c7d4000d4505f","tid":1554741,"uid":57438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:01:51.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"93e15d117f4ad5148ba2cd2c9e3cb1dc5136efc1","tid":1554741,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:07:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83e07a4a8a01fa912fd75f1124fbfe45560db1e7","tid":1554741,"uid":272188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:51:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f91a2818eda45f339e9a9bf790fe6e7b6b8c23b","tid":1554741,"uid":272188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:11:16.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"76363